videos.description: Cody White catches the pass from Brian Lewerke but he fumbles, allowing Malik Harrison to gain possession and return it 18 yards to the Michigan State 27.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Michigan State turns the ball over early) 2019/10/5

videos.headline: Michigan State turns the ball over early

videos.description: Brian Lewerke pitches the ball off to Elijah Collins but he fumbles, allowing Ohio State to recover Michigan State's second turnover in the first quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (MSU's Collins bobbles pitch, turns over the ball) 2019/10/5

videos.headline: MSU's Collins bobbles pitch, turns over the ball

videos.description: Justin Fields finds Binjimen Victor wide open on the right sideline and Victor quickly takes off running, diving for the pylon for an Ohio State 60-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Buckeyes' Victor takes Fields' pass 60 yards to the house) 2019/10/5

videos.headline: Buckeyes' Victor takes Fields' pass 60 yards to the house

videos.description: Brian Lewerke finds Darrell Stewart Jr. in the end zone for a Michigan State 20-yard touchdown in the second quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Lewerke fires pass to Stewart for 20-yard TD) 2019/10/5

videos.headline: Lewerke fires pass to Stewart for 20-yard TD

videos.description: Justin Fields completes a pass to Luke Farrell who pushes his way past Michigan State defenders for a 21-yard touchdown in the second quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Farrell fights his way into the end zone for 21-yard TD) 2019/10/5

videos.headline: Farrell fights his way into the end zone for 21-yard TD

videos.description: Justin Fields makes a quick pass to J.K. Dobbins, who finds a hole and takes off on a footrace for the end zone late in the second quarter vs. Michigan State.
videos.headline: Dobbins breaks free for 67-yard TD

videos.description: Justin Fields punches in a touchdown in the fourth quarter to extend Ohio State's lead vs. Michigan State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Fields keeps it himself for short TD) 2019/10/5

videos.headline: Fields keeps it himself for short TD

videos.description: Justin Fields throws two touchdown passes and runs for another to propel No. 4 Ohio State to a 34-10 win over Michigan State.

videos.headline: Fields leads Ohio State to win with 3 TDs
